### VagaLume API - Testes de Autenticação
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### 2. Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "Senha@123"
}

### 3. Login com usuário demo
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "demo@vagalume.com.br",
  "password": "Demo@2025"
}

### 4. Obter perfil do usuário autenticado
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.tokens.accessToken}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 5. Refresh token
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.tokens.refreshToken}}
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 6. Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
